but indistinguishable from human skin to the touch.

255
00:19:02,188 --> 00:19:04,054
这是什么封皮？
What's this cover for?

256
00:19:04,056 --> 00:19:05,856
我们在进行皮肤染色时遇到麻烦
We're having trouble getting the skin to take the dye.

257
00:19:05,858 --> 00:19:07,358
这是当然清楚的
It's naturally clear,

258
00:19:07,360 --> 00:19:10,327
而外衣有助于着色到皮肤上
and the outer suit helps the color to sink in.

259
00:19:10,329 --> 00:19:12,930
所以你想要机器士兵看起来像人类？
So you want the machine soldier to look human?

260
00:19:12,932 --> 00:19:16,333
是的，我们希望机器可以处理“三区”战争…
Yes, we want machines that can manage a three-block war...

261
00:19:16,335 --> 00:19:18,669
战斗、谈判和治安三阶段
the battle, the negotiations and the peace.

