This is what I miss the most... the feel of another human,

277
00:20:46,559 --> 00:20:48,359
人的手在我的手中
someone's hand in mine.

278
00:20:49,394 --> 00:20:51,195
嗯，你当然可以了
Um, of course you can.

279
00:20:51,197 --> 00:20:53,697
我… 我其实认为这不是一个好主意
I... I actually don't think that's a good idea.

280
00:20:53,699 --> 00:20:56,066
嗯，碳纤维的肌肉非常结实
Um, the carbon-fiber muscles are extremely strong.

281
00:20:56,068 --> 00:20:59,970
