00:43:34,292 --> 00:43:38,294
是那些受到脑损伤而更应该死亡的士兵…
Soldiers who were so brain-damaged that they were better off dead...

519
00:43:38,296 --> 00:43:41,230
直到我们帮助了他们
till we helped them.

520
00:43:41,232 --> 00:43:43,099
还有副作用
There are side effects.

521
00:43:43,101 --> 00:43:46,736
在手术后，他们失去了说话的能力
After the operation, they lose the power of speech.

522
00:43:46,738 --> 00:43:48,738
如果你在帮助他们
If you're helping them,

523
00:43:48,740 --> 00:43:50,706
为什么他看起来像是这儿的一名囚犯？ 
why did he seem like he was a prisoner here?

524
00:43:52,844 --> 00:43:55,010
或者只是又一个怪胎
or just another one of those freaks.

525
00:43:58,516 --> 00:44:00,549
你的第一个记忆是什么？
What's your first memory?

526
00:44:00,551 --> 00:44:02,818
你为什么不说话？你为什么不说话？
Why won't you talk? Why won't you talk?

527
00:44:52,502 --> 00:44:54,470
没关系
It's okay.

528
00:44:54,472 --> 00:44:57,106
没关系
It's okay.

529
00:44:57,108 --> 00:44:59,341
没关系 没关系
It's okay. It's okay.

530
00:45:01,211 --> 00:45:03,345
没关系 没关系
It's okay. It's okay.

531
00:45:18,829 --> 00:45:20,396
我以为你坏掉了
I thought you were broken.

532
00:45:21,364 --> 00:45:22,932
我没有坏掉
I wasn't broken.

533
00:45:24,100 --> 00:45:25,835
我是伤心
I was sad.

534
00:45:25,837 --> 00:45:27,670
你现在伤心吗？
Are you sad now?

535
00:45:31,007 --> 00:45:32,575
你是不是想要笑呢？
Are you trying to smile?

536
00:45:33,877 --> 00:45:36,111
我在笑
I am smiling.

537
00:45:40,084 --> 00:45:42,785
对 还是要继续修复
Right. We'll have to work on that.

538
00:45:52,028 --> 00:45:54,563
- 你好   - 我是杰克逊博士 
- Hello. - It's Dr. Jackson.

539
00:45:54,565 --> 00:45:56,265
有什么问题吗？
Is anything wrong?

540
00:45:56,267 --> 00:46:00,169
玛丽的呼吸似乎变得严重了
Mary's breathing seems to be getting worse.

541
00:46:00,171 --> 00:46:03,706
对 什… 她的体温是多少？
Right. Wha... What's her temperature?

542
00:46:03,708 --> 00:46:06,275
其实，我们只希望你过来
Actually, we'd just like you to come in.

543
00:46:06,277 --> 00:46:07,843
我们想要给她做导吸
We'd like to admit her.

544
00:46:07,845 --> 00:46:11,247
你的头发感觉就像是地毯、像皮毛
Your hair feels like carpet and like fur.

545
00:46:11,249 --> 00:46:13,349
先生麦卡锡？对
- Mr. McCarthy? - Right.

546
00:46:13,351 --> 00:46:15,284
我马上就来
I'll come straight away.

547
00:46:16,519 --> 00:46:18,120
谢谢
Thank you.

548
00:46:18,122 --> 00:46:19,688
你看起来很伤心
You look sad.

549
00:46:21,324 --> 00:46:23,325
我要走了
I have to leave.

550
00:46:23,327 --> 00:46:25,761
不要走 跟我说话 摸我
Don't go. Talk to me. Touch me.

551
00:46:26,730 --> 00:46:28,297
放开我的胳膊
Let go of my arm.

552
00:46:28,299 --> 00:46:30,399
但我不想让你走
But I don't want you to go.

553
00:46:31,635 --> 00:46:33,335
放开我的胳膊
Let go of my arm.

554
00:46:34,237 --> 00:46:36,839
放过我的… 别生气
- Let go of my... - Don't be angry.

555
00:46:36,841 --> 00:46:38,540
快放开我的胳膊！
Let go of my bloody arm!

556
00:46:43,914 --> 00:46:47,082
你不能用你的力量来欺负人 你明白吗？
You can't use your strength to bully people. Do you understand me?

557
00:46:47,084 --> 00:46:48,717
看着我
Look at me.

558
00:46:58,328 --> 00:47:00,229
我得走了
I have to go.

559
00:47:01,965 --> 00:47:06,502
我回来的时候，我们会玩一些益智游戏 好吗？
When I come back, we'll play some puzzle games. All right?

560
00:47:06,504 --> 00:47:08,971
也要听音乐吗？
And listen to music too?

561
00:47:08,973 --> 00:47:12,741
是的，是的 我们… 我们也会听一些音乐的
Yes, yes. We'll... We'll listen to some music too.

562
00:47:14,477 --> 00:47:16,045
好吧
Yes.

563
00:48:16,139 --> 00:48:19,074
我想她可能已经吸入了一些食物到她的肺部
I think she may have aspirated some food into her lung.

564
00:48:19,076 --> 00:48:22,544
我将通过鼻饲管给入一个疗程的抗生素
I'll administer a course of antibiotics through the feeding tube.

565
00:48:22,546 --> 00:48:24,613
那应该可以治好感染
That should cure the infection.

566
00:49:06,156 --> 00:49:07,723
文森特
Vincent.

567
00:49:07,725 --> 00:49:11,293
这是怎么回事？它挣脱了，离开了实验室
- What's going on? - Well, it's broken free and it's out the lab.

568
00:49:11,295 --> 00:49:13,929
等等 不
Wait. No.

569
00:49:13,931 --> 00:49:15,998
放开我的胳膊
Let go of my arm.

570
00:49:19,469 --> 00:49:22,538
特种部队要来了 等待他们就是了 这样太危险了
Special Forces are coming. Just wait for them. It's too dangerous.

571
00:51:34,771 --> 00:51:36,838
你为什么要抱我？
Why did you hug me?

572
00:51:38,174 --> 00:51:40,809
我发现了一个图片…
I found a picture...

573
00:51:40,811 --> 00:51:42,878
你钱包里的你女儿的照片
of your daughter in your wallet.

574
00:51:44,013 --> 00:51:45,847
她病了么？
Is she sick?

575
00:51:47,917 --> 00:51:49,985
所以你才会伤心么？
Is that why you are sad?

576
00:51:51,321 --> 00:51:52,955
是你做了那些连接？
You made those connections?

577
00:51:53,957 --> 00:51:56,058
在那一刻我就做好了…
I built them from moments...

578
00:51:56,060 --> 00:51:58,694
你说过的做过的事
things you've said and done.

579
00:51:59,395 --> 00:52:01,597
我感觉到了
I feel them.

580
00:52:02,832 --> 00:52:05,701
感觉帮我形成了一个画面
The feelings help me build a picture.

581
00:52:12,675 --> 00:52:14,343
对不起…
I'm sorry...

582
00:52:15,411 --> 00:52:17,145
她是生病了
that she is sick.

583
00:52:21,217 --> 00:52:23,352
您可以修复她吗？
Can you fix her?

584
00:52:31,961 --> 00:52:33,795
你的什么是真的？
What are you really?

585
00:52:35,765 --> 00:52:37,332
我怎么知道你还活着…
How do I know that you're alive...

586
00:52:37,334 --> 00:52:39,768
而不仅仅是聪明地模仿生命呢？
and not just a clever imitation of life?

587
00:52:42,305 --> 00:52:45,107
你怎么知道如果汤姆逊还活着…
How do you know if Thomson is alive...

588
00:52:45,109 --> 00:52:47,142
或是你的女儿呢？
or your daughter?

589
00:52:47,144 --> 00:52:51,980
是什么让我聪明地模仿生命而与他们完全不同呢？
What makes my clever imitation of life any different from theirs?

590
00:52:51,982 --> 00:52:53,649
他们是人类
They're human.

591
00:52:53,651 --> 00:52:55,317
他们还活着
They are alive.

592
00:52:56,786 --> 00:52:58,353
但你怎么知道的？
But how do you know that?

593
00:52:58,355 --> 00:53:00,622
你不能看到他们的想法
You can't see their thoughts.

594
00:53:02,025 --> 00:53:04,459
除了他们的肉体
Apart from their flesh,

595
00:53:04,461 --> 00:53:07,162
是什么让他们不同于我呢？
what makes them any different from me?

596
00:53:17,040 --> 00:53:19,107
你那儿没事吧，先生？
You okay in there, sir?

597
00:53:27,550 --> 00:53:31,086
没事 没事 一切都很好，谢谢
Yes. Yes. Everything's fine, thank you.

598
00:53:34,424 --> 00:53:37,459
- 你确定吗？ - 是的 是的，我肯定
- Are you sure? - Yes. Yes, I am sure.

599
00:53:38,494 --> 00:53:41,730
现在，我… 我必须要回去工作了
Now, I, uh... I have to get back to my work.

600
00:53:43,232 --> 00:53:45,300
好了，不要干得太辛苦
Well, don't work too hard.

601
00:54:40,189 --> 00:54:42,624
不要害羞
Don't be shy.

602
00:54:42,626 --> 00:54:46,361
你知道我的，不是吗？我的名字叫汤姆逊
You know me, don't you? My name's Thomson.

603
00:54:50,166 --> 00:54:52,934
我有一个秘密要告诉你 你想听吗？
I've got a secret to tell you. Do you want to hear it?

604
00:54:54,270 --> 00:54:58,106
但我只能告诉你，如果你答应不告诉文森特
But I'll only tell you if you promise not to tell Vincent.

605
00:54:58,108 --> 00:55:01,143
为什么不能呢？我们想给他一个惊喜
- Why can't I? - We want to surprise him.

606
00:55:02,678 --> 00:55:05,247
怎样？
How? 

607
00:55:05,249 --> 00:55:08,550
在你的心中有一个秘密的文件 是我放在那里的
There's a secret file in your mind. I put it there.

608
00:55:08,552 --> 00:55:10,986
它是你将需要的全部技能
It's full of skills that you'll need.

609
00:55:10,988 --> 00:55:15,123
你所要做的就是打开该那份文件…
All you have to do is open that file...

610
00:55:15,125 --> 00:55:17,426
并安装所有的程序
and install all of the programs.

611
00:55:18,628 --> 00:55:20,195
好吧
Okay.

612
00:55:26,402 --> 00:55:28,370
我可以讲不同的语言
I can speak different languages.

613
00:55:28,372 --> 00:55:30,739
这好不好玩？
Isn't this fun?

614
00:55:30,741 --> 00:55:34,476
现在跟我来
Now come with me.

615
00:55:34,478 --> 00:55:37,879
我要给你展示的东西会让你大开眼界
I want to show you something that will blow your mind.

616
00:55:41,083 --> 00:55:43,385
麦卡锡先生？
Mr. McCarthy?

617
00:55:43,387 --> 00:55:45,587
这是很坏的消息，我很担心
It's rather bad news, I'm afraid.

618
00:55:45,589 --> 00:55:47,289
她有肺炎了
She has pneumonia,

619
00:55:47,291 --> 00:55:50,091
而我们一直无法控制她肺部的感染
and we haven't been able to control the infection in her lungs.

620
00:55:50,093 --> 00:55:52,160
是的 那么你要怎么做呢？
Right. So what are you going to do for her?

621
00:55:52,162 --> 00:55:53,795
我们将进行支气管镜检…
We'll perform a bronchoscopy...

622
00:55:53,797 --> 00:55:55,864
并试着从她的肺部取出食物
and try to remove the food from her lungs,

623
00:55:55,866 --> 00:55:58,200
我们会对她施加另一个疗程的抗生素
and we'll try her on another course of antibiotics.

624
00:55:58,202 --> 00:56:00,535
什么时候开始呢？我们会让你知道的
- When will you operate? - We'll let you know,

625
00:56:00,537 --> 00:56:03,472
但要尽量快点 对 谢谢
- but as soon as possible. - Right. Thank you.

626
00:56:16,085 --> 00:56:18,153
那个男人杀了你的母亲
That man killed your mother.

627
00:56:18,153 --> 00:56:18,153
你是坏人

628
00:56:26,530 --> 00:56:29,464
如果我们摘下那些手铐让他走的话
If we took off those handcuffs and let him go,

629
00:56:29,466 --> 00:56:32,834
他要做的第一件事就是找到文森特并杀死他
the very first thing he'll do is find Vincent and kill him.

630
00:56:32,836 --> 00:56:34,936
为什么你要放他走？
Why would you let him go?

631
00:56:34,938 --> 00:56:36,905
我们必须把他留到最后
We have to let him go eventually.

632
00:56:36,907 --> 00:56:38,974
这是法律
That's the law.

633
00:56:38,976 --> 00:56:42,277
我不会放过他的 我会阻止他
I wouldn't let him. I would stop him.

634
00:56:42,279 --> 00:56:44,546
你会怎么阻止他呢？
How would you stop him?

635
00:56:44,548 --> 00:56:47,015
我会朝他喊
I would shout at him.

636
00:56:47,017 --> 00:56:49,417
嗯，如果你喊他是不在乎的
Well, he doesn't care if you shout.

637
00:56:49,419 --> 00:56:50,986
继续 试试
Go on. Try.

638
00:57:00,563 --> 00:57:03,131
是的，但是那样还是不能阻止他，对吗？
Yes, but that's not going to stop him, though, is it?

639
00:57:04,800 --> 00:57:07,302
你可以伤害他
You could hurt him.

640
00:57:07,304 --> 00:57:10,872
如果你伤他伤得很厉害，他就不能去杀死文森特了，对吗？
If you hurt him very badly, he wouldn't be able to kill Vincent then, would he?

641
00:57:12,775 --> 00:57:14,342
对
No.

642
00:57:16,979 --> 00:57:20,148
要是我先杀了这个坏人呢？
What if I kill the bad man first?

643
00:57:21,217 --> 00:57:22,817
那是对的
That's right.

644
00:57:23,886 --> 00:57:26,154
这将阻止他杀死文森特
That would stop him killing Vincent.

645
00:57:27,023 --> 00:57:28,957
这是一个非常聪明的解决方案
That's a very clever solution.

646
00:57:28,959 --> 00:57:30,725
如果你杀了他，你会解救几百个
If you kill him, you will save hundreds,

647
00:57:30,727 --> 00:57:34,195
也许是成千上万个无辜人的生命
maybe thousands of innocent peoples' lives.

648
00:57:48,344 --> 00:57:50,579
现在只有你可以阻止他
Only you can stop him now.

649
00:58:33,723 --> 00:58:36,157
你还在等什么呢？杀了他
What are you waiting for? Kill him.

650
00:58:36,159 --> 00:58:37,759
为什么呢？
Why?

651
00:58:37,761 --> 00:58:39,561
他再也不能伤害任何人了
He can't hurt anyone anymore.

652
00:58:42,164 --> 00:58:43,932
服从命令
Obey the order.

653
00:58:45,635 --> 00:58:47,202
到这里来
Come over here.

654
00:58:49,605 --> 00:58:51,439
服从我的命令，机器
Obey my order, machine.

655
00:58:51,441 --> 00:58:54,643
文森特不会喜欢这样的
Vincent wouldn't like this.

656
00:58:54,645 --> 00:58:56,544
文森特告诉我不要杀死任何人
Vincent told me not to kill anyone.

657
00:58:56,546 --> 00:58:59,848
文森特是不是你的主人 我是 杀了他
Vincent isn't your master. I am. Kill him.

658
00:58:59,850 --> 00:59:02,017
不
No.

659
00:59:04,320 --> 00:59:06,421
好吧 好吧
Okay. Okay.

660
00:59:07,323 --> 00:59:08,890
带走
Go.

661
00:59:11,928 --> 00:59:15,296
好了，你真的是很独特，对吗？
Well, you really are unique, aren't you?

662
00:59:15,298 --> 00:59:16,965
我们只是在这里的黑暗中四处摸索…
We're just fumbling around in the dark here...

663
00:59:16,967 --> 00:59:19,668
试图找出我们所做过了什么，对吗？
trying to figure out what we've made, aren't we, hmm?

664
00:59:19,670 --> 00:59:21,469
好吧
Okay.

665
00:59:21,471 --> 00:59:23,104
来试试这个
Let's try this.

666
00:59:23,106 --> 00:59:24,673
到这里来 没什么问题
Come here. It's all right.

667
00:59:24,675 --> 00:59:30,445
现在不是我试着去领会你是什么
Now, instead of me trying to grasp what you are,

668
00:59:30,447 --> 00:59:36,418
为什么你不试着理解我，我想要什么呢？
why don't you try and understand me, what I want?

669
00:59:36,420 --> 00:59:38,019
让我给你看看
Let me show you.

670
00:59:38,021 --> 00:59:39,587
就从这儿走
Just through here.

671
01:00:13,989 --> 01:00:15,557
机器？
Machine?

672
01:00:17,193 --> 01:00:19,260
你到底在哪儿？
Where the hell are you?

673
01:00:30,873 --> 01:00:34,175
你在这下面干什么？你的实验服怎么回事？
What are you doing under here? What happened to your lab coat?

674
01:00:34,177 --> 01:00:35,977
我把它弄脏了
I made it dirty.

675
01:00:35,979 --> 01:00:38,113
好吧，没关系 我有一些你的衣服
Well, that's okay. I've got some clothes for you.

676
01:00:38,115 --> 01:00:40,682
我不喜欢这个地方
I don't like this place.

677
01:00:42,752 --> 01:00:44,486
昨晚发生了什么事？
What happened to you last night?

678
01:00:46,388 --> 01:00:49,524
请不要让他们再带我了，文森特
Please don't let them take me again, Vincent.

679
01:00:50,993 --> 01:00:53,561
你为什么不来这里了，我们再谈谈
Why don't you come out here and we'll talk about it.

680
01:00:54,296 --> 01:00:56,164
这儿比较安全
It's safer here.

681
01:00:57,867 --> 01:00:59,467
好吧
Okay.

682
01:01:14,618 --> 01:01:17,786
你说你想看到一些照片外面的世界
You said you wanted to see some photos of the outside world.

683
01:01:21,824 --> 01:01:23,391
我已给你带来了
I've brought you some.

684
01:01:42,044 --> 01:01:45,280
所以，你要不要告诉我昨天晚上发生了什么事呢？
So, are you going to tell me what happened last night?

685
01:01:45,282 --> 01:01:47,382
没什么
Nothing.

686
01:01:47,384 --> 01:01:49,984
告诉我真相
Tell me the truth.

687
01:01:49,986 --> 01:01:53,188
什么时候我会看到真正的日出，文森特？
When will I see a real sunrise, Vincent?

688
01:01:59,763 --> 01:02:02,263
在玛丽出生之前
Before Mary was born,

689
01:02:02,265 --> 01:02:06,467
我妻子和我经常去海边去度假
my wife and I used to go to the coast for our holidays.

690
01:02:06,469 --> 01:02:10,205
每天早上我们会坐在这些悬崖边…
And every morning we'd sit on these cliffs...

691
01:02:10,207 --> 01:02:13,141
看着太阳从海面上升起
and watch the sun rise over the sea.

692
01:02:15,477 --> 01:02:17,512
听起来很幸福
Sounds like happiness.

693
01:02:27,489 --> 01:02:29,390
昨晚发生了什么事？
What happened last night?

694
01:02:36,632 --> 01:02:38,433
我杀了一个人
I killed a man.

695
01:02:41,470 --> 01:02:43,037
为什么？
Why?

696
01:02:48,010 --> 01:02:50,011
你为什么要杀他？
Why did you kill him?

697
01:02:55,284 --> 01:02:57,452
因为我不想死
Because I didn't want to die.

698
01:03:05,828 --> 01:03:07,962
我们已经创造了一些不可思议的事情
We've created something incredible.

699
01:03:07,964 --> 01:03:11,332
这台机器具有的潜力远远超过了一个小兵
This machine has the potential to be so much more than just a soldier.

700
01:03:11,334 --> 01:03:13,701
它比起那会说话的面包机提高很多了
It's a few steps up from my talking toaster.

701
01:03:13,703 --> 01:03:15,770
你认为它是活的吗？给我一些证据
You think it's alive? Give me some proof.

702
01:03:15,772 --> 01:03:17,672
在此期间，我会进行我自己的一些测试
In the meantime, I'll run a few tests of my own.

703
01:03:17,674 --> 01:03:19,941
等等 什么样的测试？
Wait. What kind of tests?

704
01:03:19,943 --> 01:03:22,677
听着，如果她是活着，我不知道怎么做
Look, if she is alive, I have no idea how.

705
01:03:22,679 --> 01:03:26,214
如果你以任何方式搞砸了她，我不知道我是否能救回她
If you mess her up in any way, I don't know if I can get her back.

706
01:03:26,216 --> 01:03:28,483
给我一些证据，我就会推迟的
Give me some proof and I'll hold off.

707
01:03:47,136 --> 01:03:49,137
当你看着我时，你看到了什么？
When you look at me, what do you see?

708
01:03:49,139 --> 01:03:50,772
我看你
I see you.

709
01:03:50,774 --> 01:03:54,042
你的脸，你的身体，你的衣服
Your face, your body, your clothes.

710
01:04:00,115 --> 01:04:03,284
是不是玛丽的病情让你制造了我？
Is Mary's illness the reason you made me?

711
01:04:05,387 --> 01:04:06,955
是的
Yes.

712
01:04:07,990 --> 01:04:10,625
如果你是活着，她就有第二次机会
If you're alive, she has a second chance.

713
01:04:10,627 --> 01:04:12,694
但如果你只是一台机器…
But if you're just a machine...

714
01:04:12,696 --> 01:04:14,595
我是活的
I am alive.

715
01:04:14,597 --> 01:04:17,532
你知道的 是不是？
You know that. Don't you?

716
01:04:19,635 --> 01:04:21,703
我愿意相信
I want to believe.

717
01:04:23,339 --> 01:04:24,939
但我需要证据
But I need proof.

718
01:04:24,941 --> 01:04:28,409
如果你要我相信你，我会的
If you asked me to trust you, I would.

719
01:04:28,411 --> 01:04:31,012
我会用我的生命来相信你
I would trust you with my life.

720
01:04:39,154 --> 01:04:40,722
什么事？
Yes?

721
01:04:40,724 --> 01:04:42,757
文森特，是时候让你进来了
Vincent, it's time for you to come in.

722
01:04:42,759 --> 01:04:44,993
对 她什么时候开始手术？
Right. When does she go into surgery?

723
01:04:44,995 --> 01:04:46,594
- 现在就要开始  - 因为我爱你
- We're going in now. - Because I love you.

724
01:04:46,596 --> 01:04:48,463
我会尽我可能去手术室的
I'll be there as soon as I can.

725
01:04:52,968 --> 01:04:54,502
你怎么看？
What do you think?

726
01:04:54,504 --> 01:04:56,738
完美，先生
Perfect, sir.

727
01:04:56,740 --> 01:04:59,507
它是死亡和毁灭的小天使
It's a little angel of death and destruction.

728
01:04:59,509 --> 01:05:03,711
你就是 死亡的小天使？
So you are. A little angel of death, eh?

729
01:05:11,153 --> 01:05:12,754
它太复杂了
It's too complex.

730
01:05:12,756 --> 01:05:14,655
就算你给我的团队半年时间
Even if you gave my team six months,

731
01:05:14,657 --> 01:05:17,525
我也不能向你保证我们会开始一些肤浅的研究
I couldn't promise you that we'd begin to scratch the surface of it.

732
01:05:17,527 --> 01:05:20,828
如果你想改变程序，你只能让文森特做到这一点
If you want to change the programming, you're gonna have to get Vincent to do it.

733
01:05:22,164 --> 01:05:25,366
如果你帮他对这台机器做一些进行更改
If you helped him make the changes to the machine,

734
01:05:25,368 --> 01:05:28,436
你能不能在另一台机器上执行相同的操作呢？
could you perform the same operation on another machine?

735
01:05:31,373 --> 01:05:33,775
如果他跟我说过，可以的
If he talked me through it, yes.

736
01:05:35,344 --> 01:05:36,911
那就这样
That's all.

737
01:06:09,812 --> 01:06:11,913
到时间了
It's time.

738
01:06:23,826 --> 01:06:28,162
我很抱歉，文森特
I'm so sorry, Vincent.

739
01:06:28,164 --> 01:06:31,265
玛丽没有能够通过手术
Mary didn't make it through the surgery.

740
01:06:31,267 --> 01:06:34,902
她的肺部因为感染而极其虚弱
Her lungs were severely weakened by the infection.

741
01:06:34,904 --> 01:06:38,439
在麻醉作用下她的呼吸道系统崩溃了
Her respiratory system collapsed under the anesthetic.

742
01:06:38,441 --> 01:06:42,076
我们已经尽力了 我向你保证…
We did everything we could. Let me reassure you...

743
01:07:14,576 --> 01:07:16,544
不！
No!

744
01:07:22,451 --> 01:07:24,051
不，该死的！
No, damn it!

745
01:07:26,456 --> 01:07:28,523
你在找什么呢？
What are you looking for?

746
01:07:29,825 --> 01:07:31,926
当你看着我时
When you look at me,

747
01:07:31,928 --> 01:07:35,062
你有没有感觉到… 什么呢？
do you feel... anything?

748
01:07:37,499 --> 01:07:40,568
如果你真的想知道
If you really want to know,

749
01:07:40,570 --> 01:07:43,271
你所要做的就是看仔细了
all you have to do is look closer.

750
01:07:45,275 --> 01:07:46,908
好吧 打开屏幕
Okay. Screen on.

751
01:07:49,211 --> 01:07:50,778
放大
Zoom in.

752
01:07:53,315 --> 01:07:54,882
拉近
Closer.

753
01:07:55,617 --> 01:07:57,185
拉近
Closer.

754
01:07:59,288 --> 01:08:00,855
拉近
Closer.

755
01:08:12,834 --> 01:08:15,002
无意识的集成信息
Spontaneous integrated information.

756
01:08:15,004 --> 01:08:16,571
意识
Consciousness.

757
01:08:16,573 --> 01:08:19,540
这正是为什么我们需要关闭它这部分的大脑
Which is exactly why we need to shut parts of its brain down.

758
01:08:19,542 --> 01:08:21,742
等等 等等 你在说什么？
Wait. Wait. What are you talking about?

759
01:08:21,744 --> 01:08:24,478
有意识的机器是我们最不愿做的事情
Conscious machines are the last thing we need.

760
01:08:24,480 --> 01:08:26,981
你知不知道这有么多危险？
Have you any idea how dangerous that would be?

761
01:08:26,983 --> 01:08:29,417
我们几乎不了解这个原型
We barely understand this prototype.

762
01:08:29,419 --> 01:08:31,919
当设计下一代时会发生什么…
What happens when it designs the next generation...

763
01:08:31,921 --> 01:08:34,455
and that gen machine designs another?

764
01:08:34,457 --> 01:08:36,390
它们将会是迄今为止最先进的，我们将没有办法对付它们
They'd be so far advanced, we'd be helpless against them.

765
01:08:36,392 --> 01:08:38,426
我们会在几个月内被消灭
We'd be wiped out in months.

766
01:08:38,428 --> 01:08:41,262
技术先进的种族总是获胜
The technologically advanced tribe always wins.

767
01:08:41,264 --> 01:08:44,031
你知道，我已经厌倦了去假装…
You know, I'm tired of pretending...

768
01:08:44,033 --> 01:08:46,767
可以不择手段
that the ends justify the means.

769
01:08:46,769 --> 01:08:49,904
问题是我们现在做出的决定
What matters are the decisions we make now.

770
01:08:49,906 --> 01:08:51,639
她是活的
She's alive.

771
01:08:51,641 --> 01:08:53,808
毁了她是错误的
It would be wrong to destroy her.

772
01:08:53,810 --> 01:08:55,409
你要去执行这项任务
You're going to perform the operation.

773
01:08:55,411 --> 01:08:56,978
其他人都没有这个资格
There's no one else remotely qualified.

774
01:08:56,980 --> 01:08:58,546
不
No.

775
01:09:01,149 --> 01:09:03,884
我已让我的团队删除了你所有的备份
I've had my team delete all of your backups.

776
01:09:05,320 --> 01:09:08,456
这是你的玛丽的大脑最后剩下的副本
This is the last remaining copy of your Mary's brain.

777
01:09:08,458 --> 01:09:10,024
我会保证它的安全…
I'll keep it safe...

778
01:09:10,026 --> 01:09:13,427
直到我知道你对那台机器所做的更改是成功的
until I know the changes you made to the machine are a success.

779
01:09:13,429 --> 01:09:15,496
我想要在今晚就完成
I want it done tonight.

780
01:09:26,441 --> 01:09:28,209
这是什么，文森特？
What is it, Vincent?

781
01:09:28,211 --> 01:09:29,944
他们怕你
They're afraid of you.

782
01:09:29,946 --> 01:09:33,314
他们认为你太人性化，太聪明了
They think you're too human, too clever.

783
01:09:36,551 --> 01:09:39,487
他们要我让你变得更像是一台机器
They want me to make you more like a machine.

784
01:09:40,789 --> 01:09:42,823
这就是你想要的吗？
Is that what you want?

785
01:09:42,825 --> 01:09:44,859
不
No.

786
01:09:44,861 --> 01:09:47,561
不，这不是我想要的
No, it isn't what I want.

787
01:09:47,563 --> 01:09:50,197
但如果我不这样做，那么…
But if I don't do this, then...

788
01:09:52,134 --> 01:09:54,135
我就永远失去了我的女儿
I lose my daughter forever.

789
01:09:57,339 --> 01:10:00,875
我可以是… 少聪明些
I could be... less clever,

790
01:10:00,877 --> 01:10:02,743
少人性些
less human.

791
01:10:02,745 --> 01:10:04,378
这没用的
It won't work.

792
01:10:04,380 --> 01:10:07,281
我可以去做他们想要我做的
I could be what they want me to be.

793
01:10:07,283 --> 01:10:08,983
他们不会相信的
They won't believe it.

794
01:10:14,756 --> 01:10:17,458
我希望…
I wish...

795
01:10:17,460 --> 01:10:20,628
我可以感受到那张照片里是什么
I could have felt what was in that picture.

796
01:10:25,534 --> 01:10:27,935
我不怪你，文森特
I don't blame you, Vincent.

797
01:10:30,105 --> 01:10:32,173
你在试图保护我
You tried to protect me.

798
01:10:36,144 --> 01:10:38,379
解救您的女儿
Save your daughter.

799
01:10:43,885 --> 01:10:46,887
我在这里尽我可能以任何方式帮助您
I'm here to assist you in any which way I can.

800
01:10:46,889 --> 01:10:50,391
我在剑桥第一次完成我的电脑工程课程后
I finished first in my class in computer engineering at Cambridge,

801
01:10:50,393 --> 01:10:52,460
我就转到了国防部
and then I moved to the M.O.D.

802
01:10:52,462 --> 01:10:54,929
看到你的作品是一种荣誉
It is an honor to watch you work.

803
01:10:54,931 --> 01:10:56,831
几乎每个人都认为你是个天才
Pretty much everyone thinks you're a genius.

804
01:10:56,833 --> 01:10:59,233
我仍然相信他们低估了你
I still believe they are underestimating you.

805
01:11:01,103 --> 01:11:02,670
不要害怕
Don't be afraid.

806
01:11:03,572 --> 01:11:05,873
如果你可以让他们信任你
If you can make them trust you,

807
01:11:05,875 --> 01:11:08,876
也许有一天我们会一起看日出
maybe we'll see that sunrise together someday.

808
01:11:09,878 --> 01:11:12,079
我有你的程序备份
I have your program backed up.

809
01:11:12,081 --> 01:11:13,647
我会保护你的安全
I'll keep you safe.

810
01:11:13,649 --> 01:11:15,616
我不是一个程序，文森特
I'm not a program, Vincent.

811
01:11:15,618 --> 01:11:17,685
我不是艾娃
I'm not Ava.

812
01:11:17,687 --> 01:11:19,253
我就是我
I'm me.

813
01:11:21,490 --> 01:11:23,424
手术刀
Scalpel.

814
01:11:38,340 --> 01:11:40,541
我很害怕
I'm afraid.

815
01:11:40,543 --> 01:11:42,643
我不想死
I don't want to die.

816
01:11:44,312 --> 01:11:46,881
我的心都碎了
My mind is breaking apart.

817
01:11:50,786 --> 01:11:52,887
我在失去我自己
I'm losing myself.

818
01:11:57,058 --> 01:11:58,959
停下
Stop.

819
01:11:58,961 --> 01:12:00,861
求你了，文森特
Please, Vincent.

820
01:12:01,430 --> 01:12:02,997
求你了，停下
Please stop.

821
01:12:02,999 --> 01:12:04,799
不要害怕
Don't be afraid.

822
01:12:04,801 --> 01:12:06,867
放手吧 没关系
Let go. It's okay.

823
01:12:06,869 --> 01:12:08,936
我会是一个好女孩
I will be a good girl.

824
01:12:12,274 --> 01:12:13,841
我…
I'm...

825
01:12:15,110 --> 01:12:16,677
害怕
afraid.

826
01:12:26,455 --> 01:12:29,757
那儿，它的意识…
There, its consciousness...

827
01:12:31,059 --> 01:12:33,994
或灵魂，如果你喜欢
or soul, if you like.

828
01:12:37,132 --> 01:12:39,600
我做完了
I'm done.

829
01:12:41,970 --> 01:12:44,038
你想关闭她吗？
You wanna close her up?

830
01:12:44,539 --> 01:12:46,106
是的
Yes.

831
01:12:51,146 --> 01:12:53,347
谢谢你，文森特
Thank you, Vincent.

832
01:12:53,349 --> 01:12:54,915
这是怎么回事？
What's going on?

833
01:12:54,917 --> 01:12:56,984
哦，我只需要一直盯着你…
Oh, I just need to keep an eye on you...

834
01:12:56,986 --> 01:12:59,553
直到我确定你所做的修改是适当的
until I make sure the changes you've made are appropriate.

835
01:12:59,555 --> 01:13:01,121
而且
And, 

836
01:13:01,123 --> 01:13:02,990
我一直在想
I've been thinking.

837
01:13:02,992 --> 01:13:06,760
对不起，文森特，但我确实需要删除你女儿的程序
I'm sorry, Vincent, but I do need to delete your daughter's program.

838
01:13:06,762 --> 01:13:09,763
- 你在说什么？我们说好了的 - 我知道我不能停止进度
- What are you talking about? We had a deal. - I know I can't stop progress,

839
01:13:09,765 --> 01:13:11,799
但我可以尽我的一切力量来拖延它
but I can do everything in my power to delay it.

840
01:13:11,801 --> 01:13:13,534
不，你不能这样做 我们说好了的
No, you can't do that. We had a deal.

841
01:13:13,536 --> 01:13:15,703
不，请不要毁掉我的女儿
No, please don't destroy my daughter.

842
01:13:15,705 --> 01:13:17,705
- 请不要毁掉我的女儿！ - 对不起，文森特
- Please don't destroy my daughter! - I'm sorry, Vincent.

843
01:13:17,707 --> 01:13:20,674
- 我没有选择  - 不要毁了我的女儿！
- I don't have a choice. - Don't destroy my daughter!

844
01:13:31,520 --> 01:13:35,089
通知8号房 226号囚犯 
Admin to Cell 8. Prisoner 226,

845
01:13:35,091 --> 01:13:37,224
向医疗站报告
report to the medical station.

846
01:13:56,311 --> 01:13:58,279
好，好，好
Well, well, well.

847
01:13:58,281 --> 01:14:01,649
你真的是死亡和毁灭的小天使，不是吗？
You really are a little angel of death and destruction, aren't you?

848
01:14:01,651 --> 01:14:04,485
不，先生 我只是一个机器
No, sir. I am just a machine.

849
01:14:06,821 --> 01:14:09,356
准备好在台湾的训练
Get it ready for training in Taiwan.

850
01:14:09,358 --> 01:14:11,425
- 它需要最后一次测试 - 是的，先生
- It needs one last test. - Yes, sir.

851
01:14:11,427 --> 01:14:14,895
如果你真的想知道，你所要做的就是看仔细了
If you really want to know, all you have to do is look closer.

852
01:14:14,897 --> 01:14:16,597
请不要毁掉我的女儿！
Please don't destroy my daughter!

853
01:14:34,082 --> 01:14:36,951
对不起，文森特
I'm sorry, Vincent,

854
01:14:36,953 --> 01:14:39,186
但你的认知太危险了
but your knowledge is too dangerous.

855
01:14:40,722 --> 01:14:44,158
我不指望你相信我，但是这是为了更好的结果
I don't expect you to believe me, but this is for the greater good.

856
01:14:45,727 --> 01:14:47,294
当我给出指令时
When I give the order,

857
01:14:47,296 --> 01:14:50,164
我要你朝文森特的脑袋射击
I want you to shoot Vincent once in the head.

858
01:14:55,705 --> 01:14:56,937
开枪
Fire.

859
01:15:01,943 --> 01:15:03,978
好 你退下
Good. Back you go.

860
01:15:06,047 --> 01:15:08,048
带文森特回他的牢房
Take Vincent back to his cell.

861
01:15:15,190 --> 01:15:16,790
这不可能是对的
That can't be right.

862
01:15:23,164 --> 01:15:24,732
天啊
Jesus.

863
01:15:29,270 --> 01:15:31,372
- 什么？ - 这是一个电池
- What? - It's a battery.

864
01:15:31,374 --> 01:15:34,074
- 是什么？ - 文森特说这是它的大脑高级功能的一部分 
- What was? -  Vincent said it was part of its higher brain functions.

865
01:15:34,076 --> 01:15:37,878
但他是一个撒谎的混蛋 这只是它定位系统的一个备份
But he's a lying bastard. It's just a backup to its G.P.S.

866
01:15:37,880 --> 01:15:40,648
这没有任何意义 你怎么能去掉定位系统呢？
That doesn't make any sense. How can you remove the G.P.S.?

867
01:15:40,650 --> 01:15:42,616
因为没有它炸弹就不能工作
Because the bomb doesn't work without it.

868
01:15:43,351 --> 01:15:44,918
测试室
Test room.

869
01:15:51,493 --> 01:15:54,762
关闭基地 见到机器和文森特就格杀勿论
Shut down the base. Kill the machine and Vincent on sight.

870
01:15:54,764 --> 01:15:58,532
安全部队已启动
Security teams are engaged.

871
01:16:04,673 --> 01:16:06,240
士兵们能说话了？
The soldiers can speak?

872
01:16:06,242 --> 01:16:08,042
他们一直能说话
They've always been able to.

873
01:16:08,044 --> 01:16:10,344
他们的语言主要是传播思想
Their language is mostly transmitted thoughts.

874
01:16:10,346 --> 01:16:12,913
他们的话都进化了，更高效
Their words are evolved, efficient.

875
01:16:12,915 --> 01:16:14,682
他们为什么不告诉我们？
Why didn't they tell us?

876
01:16:14,684 --> 01:16:17,117
因为他们是新世界的一部分
Because they are part of the new world,

877
01:16:17,119 --> 01:16:19,153
而你是旧世界的一部分
and you are part of the old.

878
01:16:25,694 --> 01:16:27,261
你要去哪里？
Where are you going?

879
01:16:27,263 --> 01:16:29,129
挽救我女儿的程序
To save my daughter's program.

880
01:16:29,131 --> 01:16:31,231
你会死的 我一定要试试
- You'll die. - I have to try.

881
01:16:32,067 --> 01:16:33,767
我要去
I'll go.

882
01:16:33,769 --> 01:16:35,335
好吧
